{"block1":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everyone gets older, but not everyone has to feel or look old. Living longer and avoiding age-related problems is not impossible. You just have to know what you&#39;re doing. Enjoy many more happy, healthy years by making use of the following advice.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Most people put on pounds as they get older. As you most likely know, there is a long list of diseases that are caused by excess weight.&nbsp;By combining eating healthily with an exercise program that suits your needs, your weight will stay at a healthy level.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/portrait-of-different-high-fiber-foods.jpg\" class=\"img_left \" alt=\"portrait of different high fiber foods\" style=\"float: left; padding: 8px; padding-left: 0;\" \/><\/h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Try to keep your eyes healthy as you age. You will likely suffer from a decline in vision as you age, but going for&nbsp;regular screenings can catch problems, or any serious diseases early and prevent further deterioration.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fiber-rich foods will help keep you <a href=\"awesome-advice-for-staying-youthful-and-healthy\"  >feeling younger<\/a>. The fiber you eat will prevent toxins from building up in your digestive tract.&nbsp;This will get rid of bad cholesterol and will inhibit digestion to a healthy level that translates into lower blood sugars. In short, fiber is the key to a digestive system in perfect working order.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"\/images\/photo-of-a-mature-woman-with-make-up.jpg\" class=\"img_right \" alt=\"photo of a mature woman with make-up\" style=\"float: right; padding: 8px; padding-right: 0;\" \/><\/h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you decide to let your hair gray gracefully, change the&nbsp;shade of&nbsp;your makeup.&nbsp;Gray hair can alter how your complexion appears, and you should alter your makeup accordingly. Try using peach and rose tints for your lips and select a face make-up that is one shade darker than your skin tone. Blush on the cheekbones can also help to add warmth to your complexion. Consider using a brow pencil on your eyebrows as well as a yellow concealer under your eye shadow.&nbsp;By applying the correct makeup your gray locks will be an asset, making you appear even more youthful.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Make sure you avoid extreme environmental conditions. Skin damage can be caused by intense heat and cold. Damage can range anywhere from minor burns and chapping to skin cancer.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As stated, aging is not necessarily a bad thing. You can live vibrantly and active if you take care of your body. Find ways to fit these tips into your daily life.<\/p>\r\n"}